{"title_page": "New Zealand Handball Federation", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n{{refimprove|date=July 2016}}\n\n{{Infobox national sports federations\n|assocname= New Zealand Handball Federation\n|abbrev= NZHF\n|logo= New Zealand national handball team shirt badge and association crest.png\n|logosize= 150px\n|countryflag= New Zealand\n|iocnation= New Zealand\n|url= www.handball.org.nz\n|sport= [[Handball]]\n|othersport1= [[Beach Handball]]\n|othersport2= [[Wheelchair handball]]\n|historytitle=HISTORY\n|precedingorganisationsname=\n|yearfounded= {{Start date and age|2005| | |df=y}}\n|formernames=\n|demographicstitle=DEMOGRAPHICS\n|noofclubs=\n|noofaffclubs=\n|membershipsize= \n|participationlevels= \n|affliationstitle=AFFLIATIONS\n|IF = [[International Handball Federation]]\n| IF_abbr = IHF\n| IF_joined = 2009\n|nationalolympiccom= [[New Zealand Olympic Committee]]\n|continentalassoc= [[Oceania Continent Handball Federation]]\n|nocyearjoined= \n|otheraff2= [[Commonwealth Handball Association]]\n|otheraff3= \n|otheraff4= \n|otheraff5= \n|electedtitle= GOVERNING BODY\n|patron=\n|president= Michael Roxburgh {{flagicon|NZL}}\n|sectitle= HEADQUARTERS\n|address1= [[Wellington]]\n|country= {{NZL}}\n|chiefexec= \n|secretarygeneral= Gaston Fuso {{flagicon|NZL}} {{flagicon|ARG}}\n|financetitle=FINANCE\n|companystatus=\n|operatingincome=\n|sponsors= \n}}\nThe '''New Zealand Handball Federation (NZHF)''' is the [[Sport governing body|governing body]] for the sport of [[handball]] and [[beach handball]] in [[New Zealand]]. NZHF is member of the [[Oceania Continent Handball Federation]] (OCHF), [[International Handball Federation]] (IHF) and the [[Commonwealth Handball Association]].\n\nFounded in 2005, NZHF is recognised by IHF in 2009.\n==National teams==\n* [[New Zealand national handball team]]\n* [[New Zealand women's national handball team]]\n* [[New Zealand national junior handball team]]\n* [[New Zealand national youth handball team]]\n==Region/Clubs==\n*